high_descs: Turn to the right and locate the chair.
Pick up the pencil from the back of the desk.
Carry the pencil and move a few steps to the right and turn left to still face the desk.
Place the pencil in a cup on the close side of the desk.
Pick up the cup from the desk.
Carry the cup and turn left. Go back and then turn right to find the tall dresser.
Place the cup and pencil on the top right of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup and pencil to a dresser.
